    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Secondary prints made from commercial photographic dye diffusion print products, such as Polaroid print film. The original negative is pressed onto a wet receptor such as watercolor paper, thus creating a second print from dyes leached from the photographic reagent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052948/Carr, Polaroid Transfers: Complete Guide to Image and Emulsion Transfers (1997)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052949/Grey, Photographer's Guide to Polaroid Transfer (2001)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Het maken van secundaire afdrukken met commerciële fotografische kleurenafdrukken zoals Polaroid afdrukfilm. Het originele negatief drukt men op een nat vel, bijvoorbeeld aquarelpapier, waardoor de kleurstoffen uit de fotografische reagens vrijkomen en er een tweede afdruk ontstaat. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>以寶麗來曬印膠捲一類的商業攝影用染料擴散曬印商品所製作的複製圖片。此印製法乃將原始負片壓印於水彩紙之類的濕潤接收面上，待染料從攝影用化學試劑中濾出後便可得到複製圖片。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
